  asoundpp

A simple C++ wrapper around ALSA and speex.

Dependencies:

* boost
* speex
* asound (aka alsa-lib)

Compilation:

$ git clone git://github.com/sorokin/asoundpp.git
$ cd asoundpp
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

Running examples:

$ tools/echo/echo
$ tools/speex_echo/speex_echo
